*******************************************************************             
*                                                                 *             
*    LOCKPARM - Lock routine calling parms                        *             
*                                                                 *             
*******************************************************************             
         SPACE                                                                  
@LOCKCRE RECORD BEGIN                                                           
@LOCKNAM DS    CL16          Name of the lock                                   
@LOCKFL  FLAG  ,                                                                
         FLAG  @LFSPIN       Spin type lock                                     
         END   ,                                                                
*                                                                               
@LOCKS   RECORD BEGIN                                                           
@LOCKID  DS    A             Lock id                                            
         END   ,                                                                
